    "description": "<strong>太空人遇到麻烦了！他们的太阳变成了超新星，需要你帮助建设他们的城市并设法逃避迫在眉睫的太阳灾难！<br><br>《Spacefolk City》是一款风趣而轻松的城市建设类游戏。在太空中建造飘浮的城市，用各种古怪的物品进行装饰，并让太空公民保持快乐幸福。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791710/extras/4512fbbf5287e262e464bd9983929855.poster.avif?t=1709900830\" width=380 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791710/extras/4512fbbf5287e262e464bd9983929855.webm?t=1709900830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791710/extras/4512fbbf5287e262e464bd9983929855.mp4?t=1709900830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>每个太空人都有不同的能力，而你需要创造性地利用他们的能力来确保他们生存下去。把城市装扮整洁，配备符合各人兴趣的物品，让他们保持快乐，并最大限度地提升他们在城市中的职责，以打造一个快乐的小社区！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791710/extras/e29c5e858af30e0b91eeab6bbd0848fe.poster.avif?t=1709900830\" width=380 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791710/extras/e29c5e858af30e0b91eeab6bbd0848fe.webm?t=1709900830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791710/extras/e29c5e858af30e0b91eeab6bbd0848fe.mp4?t=1709900830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>别将城市建设局限于平整的表面！享受 VR 的空间优势，在自由空间建造你的城市，在城市的上面和下面添加建筑物。同时，务必充分利用你能用来装点城市的所有无聊的东西，让你的市民们保持快乐和高产。与市民们合作，想出解决太阳危机的办法！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791710/extras/4ec7daae00e706137b221dfe8d993fa6.poster.avif?t=1709900830\" width=380 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791710/extras/4ec7daae00e706137b221dfe8d993fa6.webm?t=1709900830\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1791710/extras/4ec7daae00e706137b221dfe8d993fa6.mp4?t=1709900830\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
